CERTIFICATE OF TAX, FEE OR ASSESSMENT DUE
(Pursuant to NRS 481.081)
THE STATE OF NEVADA, DEPARTMENT OF MOTOR VEHICLES, hereinafter referred to as
Department, hereby certifies that
USTREE LLC
is liable to the State of Nevada for amounts due from and required to be paid under the provisions of
Chapter(s) 353C, 360, 366, 481, 706 of the Nevada Revised Statutes, in the amount of $4,356.03 plus
interest at the rate of 1 % per month from 06/30/2021 and any accumulating fines, penalties and interest
which may be assessed for additional violations until paid in full. The address of Ustree LLC, as it appears
on the records of the Department is:
4400 N LESLIE ST. PAHRUMP, NV 89060
P.O. BOX 1225, RIALTO, CA 92377
And that the Department has complied with all provisions of Chapter 353C, 360, 366, 481, 706 of the
Nevada Revised Statutes, when applicable, in the determination of the amounts required to be paid.
IN WITNESS THEREOF, the Department has caused this Certificate to be executed.
DATE: 06242021
STATE OF NEVADA
DEPARTMENT OF MOTOR VEHICLES
STATE OF NEVADA
) SS
CARSON CITY )
On the 24 day of _Ore
Rhonda Mckay, Revenue, Officer II
Motor Carrier Division
, 2021, Rhonda Mckay, personally appeared before a notary
public, who acknowledged that she executed the above instrument.
LOUIS LANUZA
Notary Public, State of Nevada
Appointment No. 14-13392-3
My App. Expires March 24, 2022
